<plot>On a sunny summer day the three friends Miller the bunny, Pete the dog and Rex the pig go on a journey into town. Their route takes them through a forest. There they meet Lewis the lizard who turns out to be a robber. Lewis steals the friends' money and escapes to town with his van. After spending the stolen money on luxurious goods Lewis makes a fatal encounter with aliens.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?655066</url></doc>
